OL,5,G2000 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FWith appointments lasting just 10
OL,7,     Fminutes, our GPs have the
OL,8,     Fdifficult task of deciding what to
OL,9,     Fprioritise and what can safely
OL,10,     Fwait for another day.
OL,11,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,12,     FAdam, 42, has a broken leg after a
OL,13,     Ffall at work, 22-year-old Luke has
OL,14,     Fa potentially life-threatening
OL,15,     Firregular heartbeat, and a child
OL,16,     Fstops breathing after a seizure.
